{"tid":2251303,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"大家記唔記得slut ?","createTime":"2020-10-20T16:58:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-20T17:00:28.000Z","uid":78046,"like":16,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"fd4bffd1ef8128f2ae8fd2b967d3c06f13ccf5d3","tid":2251303,"uid":78046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T16:58:15.000Z","msg":"記得嘅話 大家又記唔記得12人？ <br />\n<br />\n【網上集會：國際連動 聲援十二港人】<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"orange\">10月25（日），晚上8時正，12港人關注組將會舉辧網上集會，屆時會有嘉賓發言、家屬與主持的對談環節，大會更會播放自製影片。</span><br />\n<br />\n現時已有不同組織於當地時間10月23至25日，在全球超過30個城市舉行集會或遊行以聲援12港人及其家屬。<br />\n<br />\n網上集會將於 12港人關注組 直播播出，希望大家可以踴躍參與。<br />\n<br />\n請不要讓手足孤單，到時見。<br />\n<br />\nSource-Owen Chow<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RgzwuQo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRgzwuQo.png&h=f820e8eb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"11b7b637590d8542997912c4559e1b4e736d09a6","tid":2251303,"uid":34147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T17:00:28.000Z","msg":"SL 人 UT <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}